# Fixture WIT deps are materialized at build time by `wash build` — its
# `wit fetch` resolves the local file refs in each fixture's wkg.toml (see
# `cargo xtask build-fixtures` in /xtask). The shared p2-wit-deps/ and
# p3-wit-deps/ dirs (and the bespoke wasmcloud-bridge/ contract) are not
# matched by this pattern because they have no `wit/` subtree.
*/wit/deps/

# Lock files written by the fetch
*/wkg.lock

# Build artifacts
*/target/
target/
